OL,3,CNotts County fans to gather in Old
OL,4,CMarket Square to celebrate promotion
OL,6,FA special homecoming event will be
OL,7,Fheld on Tuesday 26 May in Nottingham
OL,8,Fto celebrate Notts County's promotion
OL,9,Fto League One after they beat Salford
OL,10,F3-0 at Wembley.
OL,12,FIt's due to begin at 3pm on Old Market
OL,13,FSquare and fans are advised to arrive
OL,14,Fno earlier than 2pm.
OL,16,FPlayers and officials will take to the
OL,17,FCouncil House balcony to show off the
OL,18,Ftrophy they won in the Play-Off Final
OL,19,Fvictory.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
