OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779804667
OL,3,CNotts County fans to gather in Old
OL,4,CMarket Square to celebrate promotion
OL,6,FThe club said the celebration is
OL,7,Fdesigned to be a family event, taking
OL,8,Fplace during school half-term.
OL,10,FThey said there is "strictly no
OL,11,Falcohol, flares, pyrotechnics or smoke
OL,12,Fbombs are permitted on to the square."
OL,14,FCllr Neghat Khan, leader of Nottingham
OL,15,FCity Council, said: "It's fantastic
OL,16,Fthat Notts County have secured
OL,17,Fpromotion and re-entered English
OL,18,Ffootball's third tier for the first
OL,19,Ftime since 2015.
OL,26,@wD@UOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
