CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779804667
OL,3,CNotts County fans to gather in Old
OL,4,CMarket Square to celebrate promotion
OL,6,F"After a rollercoaster season where
OL,7,FCounty missed out on automatic
OL,8,Fpromotion on the final day of the
OL,9,Fseason, it's incredible to see the
OL,10,Fteam secure promotion through the play-
OL,11,Foffs!
OL,13,F"On behalf of the council, I'd like to
OL,14,Fcongratulate Martin Paterson, his
OL,15,Fplayers and staff, the club's owners
OL,16,Fand board, plus the wonderful
OL,17,Fsupporters who represent our proud
OL,18,Fcity.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
