PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779804667
OL,3,CNotts County fans to gather in Old
OL,4,CMarket Square to celebrate promotion
OL,6,F"I am looking forward to attending
OL,7,FTuesday's event to celebrate with the
OL,8,Fclub, and we hope many Notts County
OL,9,Fsupporters, their families and city
OL,10,Fresidents are able to join too."
OL,12,FIn anticipation of large crowds, some
OL,13,Froad closures and diversions will be
OL,14,Fin place.
OL,16,FBus and tram services will be
OL,17,Fdisrupted between 2pm-4.30pm and will
OL,18,Fbe subject to short notice changes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@`O]
