OL,3,CNotts County fans to gather in Old
OL,4,CMarket Square to celebrate promotion
OL,6,FTram services won't serve Old Market
OL,7,FSquare or Lace Market tram stops
OL,8,Fduring the event, with trams
OL,9,Fterminating at Royal Centre and
OL,10,FNottingham train station.
OL,12,FBus stops on Friar Lane and Angel Row
OL,13,Fwill be suspended.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
